modName: More Bony Skeletons and HD skeleton clutter
summary:
An Enhanced, HD texture for your Skeleton friends and enemies.

Available in bleached and Grimy (updated fix). 

This texture will be relevant for all your human skeletons, including: creatures, skull clutter, misc. bone clutter.

Be sure to check out other InStyle Textures.
descriptionHtml:
An enhanced, HD retexture for your skeleton creatures, decorative skeletons, and also for any skeleton bones that you may have laying about.

Available in bleached and Grimy (updated to fix the grim recolor). 

Applies to human bones only.
author: jerminator
